The paper proposes a novel Bayesian optimization algorithm for model selection in the sequential setting, which is a problem commonly studied in the machine learning community. The use of deep kernel learning is also a key aspect of the proposed method. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
